  Respect LDFLAGS. #435050. Respect AR and call eqmake4 instead of qmake. Bug
  #435052

  08 Sep 2012; Markos Chandras <hwoarang@gentoo.org> recoll-1.17.3.ebuild:
  Restrict python to version 2. Bug #425492

  31 Jul 2012; Markos Chandras <hwoarang@gentoo.org> recoll-1.17.3.ebuild:
  Add missing qt-webkit dependency. Bug #428720

